<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 01:31:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>血糖水平标志着髓磷脂的生长</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/glucose-levels-signal-the-growth-of-myelin</link><description>新的研究表明，高葡萄糖水平会促使干细胞繁殖，而低水平的葡萄糖则表明它们会成熟为髓磷脂生成细胞，这一发现可能会导致治疗白质损伤和多发性硬化症的新代谢策略。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/glucose-levels-signal-the-growth-of-myelin.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 01:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/glucose-levels-signal-the-growth-of-myelin</guid></item><item><title>个人意识如何运作——并使我们独一无二</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/how-individual-consciousness-works-and-makes-us-unique</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 01:16:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/how-individual-consciousness-works-and-makes-us-unique</guid></item><item><title>已有 100 年历史的宇宙假设可能很快就会被推翻</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/100-year-old-assumption-about-the-universe-may-soon-be-overturned</link><description>物理学家长期以来一直假设宇宙在很大的尺度上是均匀的，但越来越多的证据表明这是错误的，并提出了解决一些最大的宇宙学谜团的方法&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/100-year-old-assumption-about-the-universe-may-soon-be-overturned.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 01:01:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/100-year-old-assumption-about-the-universe-may-soon-be-overturned</guid></item><item><title>理查德·费曼解释为什么过去并没有真正消失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/richard-feynman-explains-why-the-past-isnt-really-gone</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 00:46:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/richard-feynman-explains-why-the-past-isnt-really-gone</guid></item><item><title>为什么上帝在物理上不可能存在——理查德·费曼</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/why-it-is-physically-impossible-for-god-to-exist-richard-feynman</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 00:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/why-it-is-physically-impossible-for-god-to-exist-richard-feynman</guid></item><item><title>这些分子有助于生长新的脑细胞</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/these-molecules-help-grow-new-brain-cells</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 00:16:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/these-molecules-help-grow-new-brain-cells</guid></item><item><title>边部署边学习：针对通用机器人策略的舰队规模强化学习</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/learning-while-deploying-fleet-scale-reinforcement-learning-for-generalist-robot-policies</link><description>即使是训练有素的机器人在离开实验室时也会遇到困难。他们面临着“分配转变”——他们在训练中没有看到的情况，比如一个品牌的麦片粥采用了新的包装盒设计，或者一个人突然走进他们的个人空间。静态数据集（固定指令）根本无法为每个“假设”场景准备机器人。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/learning-while-deploying-fleet-scale-reinforcement-learning-for-generalist-robot-policies.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 00:01:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/learning-while-deploying-fleet-scale-reinforcement-learning-for-generalist-robot-policies</guid></item><item><title>细胞器对衰老和长寿的见解</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/organellar-insights-in-ageing-and-longevity</link><description>本综述讨论了细胞器（包括内质网、线粒体和溶酶体）作为衰老和长寿调节中代谢信号中心的作用，并强调了它们在维持细胞稳态和生物体健康方面的相互作用。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/organellar-insights-in-ageing-and-longevity2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 23:46:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/organellar-insights-in-ageing-and-longevity</guid></item><item><title>绘制大脑隐藏的创造性思维中心</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mapping-the-brains-hidden-hub-for-creative-thought</link><description>研究人员认为，头侧前额叶皮层是自发性大脑网络和执行性大脑网络之间驱动创造力的重要桥梁。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mapping-the-brains-hidden-hub-for-creative-thought.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 23:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mapping-the-brains-hidden-hub-for-creative-thought</guid></item><item><title>天然化合物显示出对抗类风湿关节炎的强大潜力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/natural-compound-shows-powerful-potential-against-rheumatoid-arthritis</link><description>一项新研究将脂肪酸代谢与类风湿性关节炎治疗联系起来，揭示了一种天然化合物，可以通过靶向以前被忽视的酶来破坏炎症。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/natural-compound-shows-powerful-potential-against-rheumatoid-arthritis2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 23:16:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/natural-compound-shows-powerful-potential-against-rheumatoid-arthritis</guid></item></channel></rss>